title: Click-Click for Children - Amazing Puzzle Game
description:
Amazing Android Puzzle Game "Click-Click for Children" it's a beautiful genre which is well suited to children and adolescents.
Your main task to collect beautiful pictures. Every next level opens new difficult and new picture which you will collect.
From 1 to 10 levels you will collect only 6 fragments in every picture.
From 11 to 24 levels you will collect 24 fragments in every picture (parents help needs for children)
Controls:
Single click changes fragment (find the right fragment)
Double click changes rotates element by 90 angles degrees

Have a good time in game.
